{"tid":2081562,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖】90後女生由管起樓到夠錢買樓","createTime":"2020-06-27T10:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T02:23:29.000Z","uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6ab44695e88415f962a9233822367b88a0b3f87e","tid":2081562,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T10:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4699672/org/38d959aced1bb7209aa073bfc0adcec5.jpg/J0DlLTfL1Mr0ETXJa9gNf-v85yDxajb2EPXydzr18nc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4699672%2Forg%2F38d959aced1bb7209aa073bfc0adcec5.jpg%2FJ0DlLTfL1Mr0ETXJa9gNf-v85yDxajb2EPXydzr18nc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b048bf99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭希娜用了6年的時間，一邊在各大地盤擔任助理管工積累經驗，一邊學習建造業的知識，拿下了理工大學的碩士文憑，良好的收入已經讓她有自信在香港「供樓」；而李鳳珍則在工料計量方面找到了樂趣，如飢似渴學習新的技術，並已經將<span style=\"color: red;\">工料測量師</span>作為事業目標。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4699715/org/278570fb66219098bc8176709353859f.jpg/0DgyLJvdzEBCTdZNlLrlyeBHIY0BpqL_w4Zo8umGaPI?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4699715%2Forg%2F278570fb66219098bc8176709353859f.jpg%2F0DgyLJvdzEBCTdZNlLrlyeBHIY0BpqL_w4Zo8umGaPI%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=1cb98a4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新輝（建築管理）有限公司人力資源總監黎兆基表示，外界有時認為在地盤工作，無非就是體力活，事實並非如此，而且近年來建造行業多了許多女性的身影，從事管工、物料計量等工種，收入豐厚、工作穩定，「不愁沒工開，只是很多人不知道如何入行。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4699736/org/5c62471cec1d5697df6e7bacdcab9c8f.jpg/zom3rwkLVKYPA5v-MAXt4qlNkYNQ7Qk20akACPupAAg?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4699736%2Forg%2F5c62471cec1d5697df6e7bacdcab9c8f.jpg%2Fzom3rwkLVKYPA5v-MAXt4qlNkYNQ7Qk20akACPupAAg%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=660a7382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎表示，學徒從第一年起就可以拿14,000元的月薪，完成學徒計劃後月薪更可以達到22,000元，而每年的人工漲幅都有10%左右。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7bdd00c9c0b969a0530e261ae244b406123bcdc","tid":2081562,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T10:14:27.000Z","msg":"佢做邊個地盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39735296a615deb65a46d034cb21ce0ada62e6ec","tid":2081562,"uid":108462,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T10:14:48.000Z","msg":"學徒從第一年起就可以拿14,000元的月薪，完成學徒計劃後月薪更可以達到22,000元<br />\n<br />\n然後夠錢買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最緊要係靠父幹"},{"pid":"d347631101cea18e940bbfae68d4b123b3116742","tid":2081562,"uid":57862,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T10:15:46.000Z","msg":"又水人入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b9adf1a7da4c027b23ab51c59cdf4e0b43045b","tid":2081562,"uid":44831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T10:17:20.000Z","msg":"拖慢黎做，做到人地俾三工，變大白象。自己就肥肥白白"},{"pid":"273728bf42e65437e74180fb58dad0b5b5168090","tid":2081562,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d347631101cea18e940bbfae68d4b123b3116742","tid":2081562,"uid":57862,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T10:15:46.000Z","msg":"又水人入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T10:17:29.000Z","msg":"關你咪事 影響到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ea48d4d817225fa6b3c49896e1133bd15056e5","tid":2081562,"uid":33437,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T10:20:02.000Z","msg":"有足夠的自信供樓，<br />\n咁佢供咗未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb13d128444f46e79700adc5f9f49f5602e8173","tid":2081562,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T10:20:50.000Z","msg":"碩士文憑<br />\n<br />\n買到樓有幾奇<br />\n<br />\n其他行業有碩士收都唔低啦<br />\n<br />\n大把老師有碩士都買到樓<br />\n<br />\n咁都好吹？"},{"pid":"3bd5be514f30db127029846